item_data.description: Our creamy and delicious aji amarillo salsa is a must have for any kitchen! Aji amarillo is the most utilized and versatile pepper in Peru. Our classic recipe of aji amarillo, dairy and lime is a show stopper! Available in a 7oz jar.
